<h4><b id="internal-source-marker_0.7285621159244329" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: medium; font-weight: normal; ">
<h3 dir="ltr"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">User Guide</span></h3><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">Extension is based on image collections. Each collection can be used for banner or slider creation.</span><br /><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; "></span><br /><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">To Install</span><br /><b id="internal-source-marker_0.7285621159244329" style="font-weight: normal; ">
<ol style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; display: inline !important; ">
<li style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; display: inline !important; "><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">extract zip archive to Magento folder </span></li></ol></b><br /><b id="internal-source-marker_0.7285621159244329" style="font-weight: normal; ">
<ol style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; display: inline !important; ">
<li style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; display: inline !important; "><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">log out of admin area and then Log In</span></li></ol></b><br /><b id="internal-source-marker_0.7285621159244329" style="font-weight: normal; ">
<ol style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; display: inline !important; ">
<li style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; display: inline !important; "><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">clear your Magento cache</span></li></ol></b><br /><b id="internal-source-marker_0.7285621159244329" style="font-weight: normal; ">
<ol style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; display: inline !important; ">
<li style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; display: inline !important; "><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">check if CMS =&gt; &ldquo;Promo Slider Banner&rdquo; section is created in admin area</span></li></ol></b><br /><b id="internal-source-marker_0.7285621159244329" style="font-weight: normal; ">
<ol style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; display: inline !important; ">
<li style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; display: inline !important; "><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">check section &ldquo;MagenMagic Extensions&rdquo; in &ldquo;System&rdquo; =&gt; &ldquo;Configuration&rdquo;</span></li></ol></b><br /><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; "></span><br /><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">Add Image Collections </span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; "></span><br /><b id="internal-source-marker_0.7285621159244329" style="font-weight: normal; ">
<ol style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; display: inline !important; ">
<li style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; display: inline !important; "><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">create image collections, that will be used for your Banners or Sliders</span></li></ol></b><br /><b id="internal-source-marker_0.7285621159244329" style="font-weight: normal; ">
<ol style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; display: inline !important; ">
<li style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; display: inline !important; "><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">CMS =&gt; Promo Slider Banner =&gt; Add Category</span></li></ol></b><br /><b id="internal-source-marker_0.7285621159244329" style="font-weight: normal; ">
<ol style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; display: inline !important; ">
<li style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; display: inline !important; "><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">after category is created - click Edit button to add images</span></li></ol></b><br /><b id="internal-source-marker_0.7285621159244329" style="font-weight: normal; ">
<ol style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; display: inline !important; ">
<li style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; display: inline !important; "><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">upload all images that will be used in future</span></li></ol></b><br /><b id="internal-source-marker_0.7285621159244329" style="font-weight: normal; ">
<ol style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; display: inline !important; ">
<li style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; display: inline !important; "><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">check and &ldquo;Save Current to this library&rdquo; - to add specific images to current catalogue</span></li></ol></b><br /><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">*in order to add links to banner - add links in full format and click &ldquo;Save Images Links&rdquo;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; "></span><br /><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">Add banner slider to any CMS page</span><br /><b id="internal-source-marker_0.7285621159244329" style="font-weight: normal; ">
<ol style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; display: inline !important; ">
<li style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; display: inline !important; "><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">go to Page in CMS section and click to the page, choose Content </span></li></ol></b><br /><b id="internal-source-marker_0.7285621159244329" style="font-weight: normal; ">
<ol style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; display: inline !important; ">
<li style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; display: inline !important; "><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">in Editor chose place you would like to add your banner and click to &ldquo;Insert Widget&rdquo; icon</span></li></ol></b><br /><b id="internal-source-marker_0.7285621159244329" style="font-weight: normal; ">
<ol style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; display: inline !important; ">
<li style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; display: inline !important; "><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">Select widget type &ldquo;Promo banner slider&rdquo; and choose all needed options.</span></li></ol></b><br /><b id="internal-source-marker_0.7285621159244329" style="font-weight: normal; ">
<ol style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; display: inline !important; ">
<li style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; display: inline !important; "><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">Add widget and save page.</span></li></ol></b><br /><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; "></span><br /><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">Add banner slider to any other page</span><br /><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">You can also add Banner or Slider to any other page of your custom template. In order to do that you have to create static block (CMS =&gt; Static Blocks). Create any static block, add there a widget &ldquo;Promo slider banner&rdquo; as a content, and remember &ldquo;Identifier&rdquo;, it will be needed.</span><br /><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; "></span><br /><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">After that open any template file, and add this code:</span><br /><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; "></span><br /><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">&lt;block type="cms/block" name="BannerSlider"&gt;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; "> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;action method="setBlockId" &gt;&lt;block_id&gt;</span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">Identifier</span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">&lt;/block_id&gt;&lt;/action&gt;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; "> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/block&gt;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; "></span><br /><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; ">IMPORTANT: change Identifier to Identifier from your static block.</span></b>
